ğŸ”§ API Endpoints
POST /api/generate-mantra
Generates a personalized mantra based on user input.

Request Body:

json
{
  "name": "string",
  "lesson": "string",
  "fear": "string"
}
Response:

json
{
  "proTip": "string with HTML formatting",
  "mantra": "string with HTML formatting"
}
GET /health
Health check endpoint to verify server is running.

