ğŸ’¡ How the Mantra System Works
Template Processing
The application uses intelligent input processing:

Lessons: Transforms common phrases like "Google is my friend" into professional concepts

Fears: Converts specific worries like "debugging" into broader challenges

Grammar: Ensures natural sentence flow with proper articles and phrasing

Example Transformations
"google is my friend" â†’ "resourcefulness in finding solutions"

"debugging" â†’ "complex debugging challenges"

